 &lt;p&gt;Beini is a small Linux distribution that packs a punch. it is based on Tiny Core Linux. It offers an array of WiFi security audit tools. Beini is easy for newbie to used compare to BackTrack, which is the popular system used to crack WEP/WPA. Beini include packages: Minidwep, Aircrack, Inflator, Reaver, Feeding Bottle, Wifite&lt;/p&gt;
